Hacking a Chromecast with Catt

Find a chromecast:

catt scan


To cast an image or a gif:

catt cast ./mygif.gif

To cast a remote video:

catt cast "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"

To cast a local video:

catt cast ./myvideo.mp4

To cast a website:

catt cast_site https://mysite.com

To add videos to the queue:

cat add "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"
